label\">Framework</span><span class=\"value\">Next.js 14</span></div>\n    <div class=\"row\"><span class=\"label\">Runtime</span><span class=\"value\">Node.js 20</span></div>\n    <div class=\"row\"><span class=\"label\">Hosting</span><span class=\"value\">AWS CloudFront + ECS</span></div>\n  </div>\n  <h2>NFR Profile</h2><div class=\"section\">\n    <div class=\"row\"><span class=\"label\">Availability</span><span class=\"value\">99.9%</span></div>\n    <div class=\"row\"><span class=\"label\">Throughput</span><span class=\"value\">10,000 concurrent users</span></div>\n    <div class=\"row\"><span class=\"label\">Latency</span><span class=\"value\">p99 < 500ms</span></div>\n    <div class=\"row\"><span class=\"label\">Data Classification</span><span class=\"value\">pii</span></div>\n    \n    \n  </div>\n  <h2>Related Entities (7)</h2><div class=\"section\">\n    <table class=\"rel-table\"><thead><tr><th>Direction</th><th>Type</th><th>Entity</th><th>Protocol</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n    <tr><td style=\"color:#0F7173;\">outbound</td><td>container_of</td><td>Claims Web UI</td><td style=\"color:#94A3B8;\">—</td></tr><tr><td style=\"color:#0F7173;\">outbound</td><td>container_of</td><td>Claims Mobile BFF</td><td style=\"color:#94A3B8;\">—</td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"color:#94A3B8;\">inbound</td><td>uses</td><td>Claims Adjuster</td><td style=\"color:#94A3B8;\">—</td></tr><tr><td style=\"color:#94A3B8;\">inbound</td><td>uses</td><td>Policyholder</td><td style=\"color:#94A3B8;\">—</td></tr><tr><td style=\"color:#94A3B8;\">inbound</td><td>realized_by</td><td>First Notice of Loss</td><td style=\"color:#94A3B8;\">—</td></tr><tr><td style=\"color:#94A3B8;\">inbound</td><td>uses</td><td>Member</td><td style=\"color:#94A3B8;\">—</td></tr><tr><td style=\"color:#94A3B8;\">inbound</td><td>uses</td><td>External Vendor</td><td style=\"color:#94A3B8;\">—</td></tr>\n    </tbody></table>\n  </div>\n  <h2>Compliance Status (1 findings)</h2><div class=\"section\">\n    <div class=\"finding finding-warning\"><span class=\"severity sev-warning\">warning</span> <span style=\"color:#94A3B8;font-size:12px;margin-left:8px;\">WCAG-001 · standard.api-design</span><p style=\"font-size:13px;margin:8px 0 0 0;\">Claims Portal has 7 WCAG 2.1 AA accessibility violations: missing alt text on 3 images, insufficient color contrast on 2 buttons, missing form labels on 2 inputs.</p></div>\n  </div>\n  <h2>Recent Signals (1)</h2><div class=\"section\"><div class=\"signal\"><strong style=\"font-size:14px;\">Claims Portal — Frontend Bundle Size Regression</strong><div style=\"color:#94A3B8;font-size:12px;margin-top:4px;\">New Relic · medium</div><p style=\"font-size:13px;margin:8px 0 0 0;\">Claims Web UI bundle size increased 34% (from 1.2MB to 1.6MB) after recent dependency update. Page load time p95 increased from 2.1s to 3.4s. Recommend tree-shaking audit.</p></div></div>\n  <div class=\"footer\">Generated by EAMS · 2026-04-02T05:40:18.446Z</div>\n</div></body></html>"
